OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight mist soon
OL,6,Fclearing this morning. Then all parts
OL,7,Fwill have a dry day with long sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Becoming very warm or hot
OL,9,Falthough somewhat cooler along the
OL,10,Feast coast. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be dry with lengthy
OL,15,Fclear periods and the odd mist patch.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,18,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Very warm
OL,19,For hot. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
