OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand bright few days although some
OL,7,Fcloud across the north and east at
OL,8,Ftimes. Becoming cooler but still quite
OL,9,Fwarm, especially in the south.
